[§ 33112. Repealed. Pub. L. 112–141, div. C, title I, § 31313(2), July 6, 2012, 126 Stat. 772]
Section, Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e), July 5, 1994, 108 Stat. 1087, related to insurance reports and information.
Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries Effective Date of RepealRepeal effective Oct. 1, 2012, see section 3(a) of Pub. L. 112–141, set out as an Effective and Termination Dates of 2012 Amendment note under section 101 of Title 23, Highways.
